Robert TRIEBE, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
STATE of New Jersey, New Jersey State Department of Transportation, Defendants-Respondents,
and
County of Somerset, Township of Bridgewater; Borough of Raritan ; John Doe 1-10; Jane Doe 1-10; John Doe Corp. 1-20, Fictitious Names, Defendants. (Unilever United States, Inc. - Movant) M-1498 September Term 2017
080981 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 20, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal is granted and the matter is summarily remanded to the Superior Court, Appellate Division to consider on the merits. Jurisdiction is not retained.
